edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.controller

Class UserController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.controller.UserController

  • @RestController
 @ExposesResourceFor(value=GoogleUser.class)
 @RequestMapping(value="/users")
 @PreAuthorize(value="hasRole(\'ROLE_ADMIN\')")
public class UserController
extends Object
    Controller for the "GoogleUser" entity. Not required to contain any connections to other entities. This is the most restricted endpoint, only the admin has access.
